      Returns:
      a 2D array of parsed values

    • resolveNulls

      public String[] resolveNulls(String[] row)
      Replace null entries in a parsed CSV row with empty strings to avoid NullPointerExceptions when joining or writing rows.
      Parameters:
      row - a parsed CSV row
      Returns:
      the same row instance with nulls replaced by ""
